  </div>
  <div id="h2hResult"></div>
</div>

<div class="picks-section">
  <h2>2026 Category Picks</h2>
  <div class="picks-grid" id="picks"></div>
</div>

<div class="perf-section">
  <h2>Total Return Performance: Top Dividend ETFs</h2>
  <div class="perf-wrap">
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>ETF</th><th>Strategy</th><th>1-Year</th><th>3-Year Ann.</th><th>5-Year Ann.</th><th>10-Year Ann.</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody id="perfBody"></tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  <p style="color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:12px;margin-top:8px">Total returns include reinvested dividends. Data as of March 2026. Past performance does not guarantee future results.</p>
</div>

<div class="strategy-section">
  <h2>Dividend ETF Strategy Guide</h2>
  <div class="strategy-cards" id="strategies"></div>
</div>

<div class="faq-section">
  <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
  <div id="faq"></div>
</div>

<div class="related-section">
  <h2>Related Tools &amp; Research</h2>
  <div class="related-grid">
    <a class="related-card" href="/etf-expense-ratios">
      <h3>ETF Expense Ratios</h3>
      <p>Compare fees across 86 major ETFs — find the cheapest funds in every category.</p>
    </a>
    <a class="related-card" href="/best-monthly-dividend-etfs">
