      <p>See how reinvesting dividends compounds your wealth over time.</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="methodology">
  <h2>Methodology</h2>
  <p>Dividend yields are trailing 12-month yields sourced from official fund documentation and verified against issuer websites. Expense ratios reflect the most current prospectus data as of Q1 2026. AUM figures are approximate and fluctuate with market conditions.</p>
  <p>Total return data includes reinvested dividends and is sourced from Morningstar. Performance figures beyond 1 year are annualized. All 21 ETFs were selected based on AUM, trading volume, and relevance to dividend-focused investors.</p>
</div>

<div class="disclaimer">This site provides data for informational purposes only. Not investment advice. Past performance does not guarantee future results.</div>

</div>
